<p>SCP-173-FR的歌词如下：</p>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><em>Sa jimali-taminy, Ge devi ma, ge devi<br />
Sa mifu-tchi puve saj kali, dey mija<br />
Kanevem nave ti pamo, nur hitve go<br />
Nan kali sal oyuve, mizuvem rep kal</em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><em>Go ve nave sa doru-rala, jahitoleni<br />
Go ve kel go der sa taminy paluvi, ilivem go<br />
Men lula-furanu ikawi, meil nan liu ?<br />
Ban men erle yuvi, dey joniva</em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><em>Nul uv'n me yulel, pom cufeve'n da<br />
Nul uv wa nan kali, mizuvem rep Erle.</em></span></p>
